# Next.js 16 and project context

- **Next.js 16** differs from older docs and from training cutoffs. Before changing App Router APIs, `next.config`, or file layout, read the bundled guide under `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` and respect deprecation notices.
- **Ralph Monitor** is an internal dashboard for Ralph AI conversations (see root layout metadata).
- Use path aliases from the codebase: `@/components`, `@/lib`, `@/components/ui` (see `components.json`).
